<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- fwqa ạlṣlyb ậh yạ ḥbyb ḥamlta ạlậtẖạma ʿny ạ̉nạ
 bijal̊diⁿ whuz̊ʾiⁿ qd̊ ʿayarwka wbạlmasạmyr qd qydwk
 ( fmawtuka njạty wdamuka fdạỷy fwqa ạlṣlybi ậh yạ ḥbyb)2
 2- fwqa ạlṣlyb ậh yạ ḥbyb ḥamlta ạlʿạra wạ̉nta ạlbạr
 bạlḥrbẗi qd ṭaʿanūka btạj iạlsẖwki qd kllwka
 ( fmwtuka njạty wdamuka fdạỷy fwqa ạlṣlybi ậh yạ ḥbyb)2
 3- fwqa ạlṣlyb ậh yạ ḥbyb dẖuqta ạlmwta ltuʿṭyny ạlḥyạẗ
 fwqa ạlṣlybi ậh yạ ḥbyby ḥamalta ạlkẖṭyẗ wạ̉nta ạlạ̹lh
 ( fmwtuka njạty wdamuka fidạyỉy fwqa ạlṣlybi ậh yạ ḥbyb)2</lyrics>
<title>fwq ạlṣlyb ậh yạ ḥbyb</title>
